{"id":148514,"type":6,"name":"刀神","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/84/d0/148514_921A3.jpg","summary":"年少氣盛的丁鵬(劉松仁)約戰殺父仇人，然其秘籍反落入奸人之手。失意之際，他幸得魔教相助，贈其彎刀一把，遂練成絕世武功，並與溫柔美麗的魔教後人青青 (趙雅芝)締結良緣。 然仙境般的忘憂谷，卻洗不去鵬追逐名利、報仇之心。他於是重出江湖，藉彎刀之神威，爭奪武林盟主之位。其後，鵬更挑戰昔日天下第一劍謝曉鋒，幾陷入其義女謝小玉的圈套，令魔教遭受株連，連妻子也性命不保。 最後，鵬雖廢玉之武功，但已與青陰陽相隔。至此，鵬悟通塵世一切名利、恩仇，皆為過眼雲煙，遂毀彎刀，退隱江湖，不問世事‧‧‧‧‧‧","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>刀神</li><li><span>原作: </span><a href=\"/person/16836\">古龍</a></li><li><span>监制: </span><a href=\"/person/16649\">李鼎倫</a></li><li><span>编审: </span><a href=\"/person/16687\">王晶</a></li><li><span>主题歌演出: </span><a href=\"/person/16551\">甄妮</a><春雨彎刀></li><li><span>主演: </span><a href=\"/person/16626\">劉松仁</a>、<a href=\"/person/16600\">趙雅芝</a>、<a href=\"/person/19727\">甘國衛</a>、<a href=\"/person/17060\">韓馬利</a>、 <a href=\"/person/16603\">石堅</a>、<a href=\"/person/16929\">高妙思</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>圆月弯刀</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>God of Sabre</li><li><span>集数: </span>12</li><li><span>开始: </span>1979年</li><li><span>类型: </span>古裝武俠</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>香港</li><li><span>电视台: </span>TVB</li><li><span>编剧: </span>譚嬣</li><li><span>编导: </span>李鼎倫</li>","eps":[{"id":572718,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/572718","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":572719,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/572719","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":572720,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/572720","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":572721,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/572721","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":572722,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/572722","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":572723,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/572723","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","